{"tid":1573544,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"害死班狗嘅根本就係林鄭","createTime":"2019-09-16T04:35:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:39:33.000Z","uid":117127,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b43730766a5cba76fc5e7da1b1260dd5b47dbd8c","tid":1573544,"uid":117127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:35:48.000Z","msg":"其實林鄭真係害死班無腦狗 如果由一開始612就成立獨立調查委員會 根本涉事警察就得10零20個 但就死都唔成立 依加差唔多近一半嘅狗都係身有屎 我當林鄭真係堅持得住 <br />\n咁下任政府或下下任呢 我好肯定香港人嘅怒氣係唔會隨時間而平息 總有一任政府會頂唔順清算你地班狗 林鄭自己都只係夠膽保證自己任內唔會清算班狗 你班仆街狗即管打啦 一係就大大力打死香港人 唔係清算總會有一日嚟 香港人頂住"},{"pid":"a778657e6d93d98bead150afbfc922d9dfea09f6","tid":1573544,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/so4yF19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fso4yF19.jpg&h=481fa700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n921民間活動<br />\n下午1:00機場交通壓力測試<br />\n晚上7:00毋忘721元朗恐襲<br />\n928民間活動<br />\n下午1:00機場交通壓力測試<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkpicnic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkpicnic&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=be85f716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkpicnic</a><br />\n【訂閱野餐頻道】 @hkpicnic<br />\n✅ 接收各種活動資訊<br />\n✅ 如何安全地發夢<br />\n✅ 逃生、自衛等有用貼士"},{"pid":"83bb87a56a330329e12947b10d69ed812136cac4","tid":1573544,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:37:46.000Z","msg":"林鄭處事能力= 0"},{"pid":"c99f0b787d2cce572b2f28ed0f9a39c56d950591","tid":1573544,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:38:06.000Z","msg":"班狗咁聽話梗係要繼續利用，錢香港大把，做就你班前線做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d54d2daac218e905cb34b010208e1561f93a08","tid":1573544,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:39:06.000Z","msg":"下屆政府就唔關事啦, 係林鄭話保班差佬姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513b66afd66